messages.content: en un texto legal como "Mi renuncia se hará efectiva a partir del día 13/05/2023", que se puede concluir: el último día de trabajo es el día 12 o 13?

The text does not specify the exact day on which the resignation will take effect, so it cannot be concluded that the last day of work is either 12 or 13. It simply states that the resignation will take effect on 13 May 2023, but it does not specify which day of the week that is.
